# Next.js App Router Rules (Strict)
- Use Next.js 15+ App Router only (app/ directory).
- Prefer Server Components by default. Add "use client" only when interactivity is required.
- Use Server Actions for mutations.
- File conventions: page.tsx, layout.tsx, loading.tsx, error.tsx.
- Dynamic routes use [slug] folders + async params/searchParams.
- All routing must be file-based (no React Router unless explicitly migrating).
- Optimize for Vercel deployment.